，\n是我與工作人員，還有各位聽眾一起創造的節目","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event143-07-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"我希望今後也能繼續帶給大家\n能夠傾聽彼此意見的感覺","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event143-07-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"（小芙……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event143-07-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"透過這個節目把PasPale的名聲傳遞到全日本，\n讓更多的人們知道PasPale的存在……\n然後再一步一步漸漸取得天下！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event143-07-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"說得好耶～小芙！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"m